---
import ContentPageLayout from '../layouts/ContentPageLayout.astro';
---

<ContentPageLayout
  title="Special Occasions"
  description="Celebrate life's milestones at Meadowlark Ranch — anniversaries, birthdays, reunions, and celebrations of life in a stunning Boulder County, Colorado setting."
  heroLabel="Events"
  heroImage="/images/special-occasions-hero.webp"
  breadcrumbs={[{label: 'Home', href: '/'}, {label: 'Events'}, {label: 'Special Occasions'}]}
  cta={{title: 'Celebrate With Us', text: 'Let us help you create a celebration as unique and meaningful as the milestone it honors.', buttonText: 'Start Planning', buttonLink: '/contact'}}
>
  <section class="content-section section--cream">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Moments Worth Remembering</h2>
      <p class="content-section__text">Life's most meaningful occasions deserve a setting that matches their significance. At Meadowlark Ranch, we craft bespoke celebrations that honor your unique story — surrounded by the beauty of the Colorado foothills and the warmth of genuine hospitality.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section section--white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section__grid">
        <div>
          <h2>Anniversaries</h2>
          <p class="content-section__text">Mark the milestones of your love story in a setting that speaks to romance and timelessness. Whether you are celebrating your first year or your fiftieth, Meadowlark Ranch provides an intimate backdrop for honoring the journey you have shared — complete with elegant dining, horse-drawn carriage rides, and mountain views that take your breath away.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-section__image">
          <img src="/images/anniversary-dinner.webp" alt="Anniversary celebration at Meadowlark Ranch" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section__grid content-section__grid--reverse">
        <div>
          <h2>Birthdays &amp; Milestone Celebrations</h2>
          <p class="content-section__text">From sweet sixteen gatherings to landmark birthdays, Meadowlark Ranch transforms every celebration into an unforgettable experience. Our team designs each event to reflect the personality and passions of the guest of honor, with custom catering, entertainment, and activities.</p>
          <p class="content-section__text">Imagine a surprise party at sunset in our covered pavilion, a gourmet dinner in the barn, or an afternoon of horseback experiences followed by fireside conversation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-section__image">
          <img src="/images/birthday-celebration.webp" alt="Birthday celebration at the ranch" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section section--white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section__grid">
        <div>
          <h2>Family Reunions</h2>
          <p class="content-section__text">Bring your family together in a place that invites connection and shared adventure. Meadowlark Ranch offers ample space for multi-generational gatherings, with activities that engage every age — from guided ranch tours and horse interactions for the little ones, to wine tastings and scenic walks for the adults.</p>
          <p class="content-section__text">Our team handles all the logistics so you can focus on what matters most: being together.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-section__image">
          <img src="/images/ranch-photo-2.webp" alt="Family reunion at Meadowlark Ranch" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section__grid content-section__grid--reverse">
        <div>
          <h2>Celebrations of Life</h2>
          <p class="content-section__text">When it is time to honor a life beautifully lived, Meadowlark Ranch provides a serene and dignified environment for remembrance and celebration. Our peaceful grounds, gentle horses, and compassionate staff create a space where family and friends can gather, reflect, and find comfort in one another.</p>
          <p class="content-section__text">We work sensitively with families to design a tribute that captures the spirit of their loved one, whether through a quiet gathering or a grand celebration.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-section__image">
          <img src="/images/horses-field.webp" alt="Peaceful setting at Meadowlark Ranch" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ContentPageLayout>
